Staff-only roles (server, host, kitchen, bar, staff) see a filtered sidebar showing only their permitted pages. Never hardcode the full sidebar for all users — always derive it from the current role. Kitchen sees all order items. Bar sees only drink-category items.

### Multi-Location

One owner login can manage multiple restaurant locations. Each restaurant is a separate row in the restaurants table with its own data. On web, a dropdown in the sidebar (RestaurantSwitcher) lets the owner switch between locations. On mobile, a switcher screen appears before the dashboard loads. All queries are scoped to the currently selected restaurant_id.

