### Customer Experience — Mobile

### Discovery

Default view is a map (Google Maps) showing nearby restaurants. Customers can switch to a list view with recommended restaurants. A search bar lets them search by name or cuisine. Filters allow narrowing by cuisine type, price range, distance, rating, dietary options, and availability. An AI chat button opens the personal dining assistant.

### AI Chat — Customer

The customer AI assistant helps with: finding restaurants near them, budget planning (e.g. "I have $100 for a date night"), recommending based on dietary preferences or occasion, answering menu questions for a specific restaurant, and helping plan events. Powered by the ai-chat Edge Function.

### Booking Flow (7 steps)

-   Step 1 — Select date

-   Step 2 — Select time slot (from get-availability edge function)

-   Step 3 — Select table from floor plan (optional — can skip to auto-assign)

-   Step 4 — Pre-order from menu (optional — menu_items where is_preorderable = true)

-   Step 5 — Review booking summary + special requests + occasion

-   Step 6 — Payment (deposit if required, pre-order total, or free) — Stripe, Apple Pay, Google Pay

-   Step 7 — Confirmation with confirmation_code displayed in monospace font

### QR Code Dine-In Ordering

When a customer scans a QR code at a table (tables.qr_code_url), the mobile app opens an ordering flow: browse the full menu, add items with modifiers, review cart, pay via Stripe. Order goes directly to the kitchen (orders + order_items, realtime). No reservation required. Customers can order as a guest (no account) — orders.is_guest_checkout = true, no loyalty points earned, payment entered manually each time.

### Loyalty Points

Customers earn points on every transaction processed through Seatly. Points accumulate in the guests.loyalty_points_balance field and are tracked in loyalty_transactions. Customers can redeem points for:

-   Free menu items — redeem points to cover the cost of specific menu items

-   Discounts off their bill — apply points as a dollar discount at checkout

-   Free event tickets — redeem points to attend restaurant events


  Loyalty tier system (Bronze/Silver/Gold/etc.) is NOT finalised. Do not hardcode tier names anywhere. Use guests.loyalty_tier field — value comes from DB. VIP early reservation access is NOT part of the redemption system.

