### Known DB Gotchas — Read This Before Querying

-   Table is named reservations — NOT bookings

-   Table status default is "empty" — NOT "available"

-   reserved_at is a single timestamptz — NOT separate date and time columns

-   shifts = service config (slot durations). staff_shifts = who is working when. Different tables.

-   Restaurant hours are in hours_json JSONB — there is NO restaurant_hours table

-   Use cover_photo_url for restaurant images — ignore cover_image_url (duplicate, will be removed)

-   Money is stored as decimal dollars (24.99) — NOT cents (2499)

-   user_restaurant_roles has no "customer" role — absence of a row = customer

-   floor_plans.layout is JSONB with structure {walls: [], tables: [], decorations: []}

-   orders.reservation_id is required (not nullable) — every order must have a reservation

